    "content": "<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body class=\"tei-surface3\" id=\"srcD_surface_b59r\"><div class=\"content \"><pb-facs-link emit=\"transcription\" facs=\"https://ores.klassik-stiftung.de/digilib/Scaler/IIIF/gsa!Arbeitskopie!71!75097!75097_117\" style=\"float: right; margin-top: -2em;\">b59r</pb-facs-link><div id=\"srcD_surface_b59r\" class=\"transkriptionField\" style=\"\"><div id=\"srcD_zone_b59r_div2_d2e45\" style=\"padding-top:5em;padding-bottom:5em;\" class=\"singleBlock textBlock \" debug-msg=\"test\" data-debug=\"1\"><div id=\"srcD_zone_b59r_fw_d2e26\" class=\"fw-top-left\" style=\"\"><span class=\"tei-fw4\"><span id=\"b59r_fw_d2e26\" class=\"top-left N_pencil\">59</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"b59r_fw_d2e26\"><p><span style=\"font-style: italic;\"><pb-i18n key=\"myapp.hand.N_pencil\">\n                            key not found: myapp.hand.N_pencil</pb-i18n></span></p></pb-popover></span></div><div id=\"srcD_zone_b59r_fw_d2e29\" class=\"fw-top-right\" style=\"\"></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb1\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb1\" duration=\"5000\">1</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">Abzeichen des mühsameren Stoffwechsels, des ringenden, schwerer arbeitenden Lebens.) Man \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb2\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb2\" duration=\"5000\">2</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">sehe sich die Zeiten eines Volkes an, in denen der Gelehrte <span class=\"insertionMark right  insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">in den</span></span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l8l6\" class=\"hatching\">im</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l8l6\"><span class=\"transcription\">im</span></pb-popover> Vordergrund<span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l8l8\" class=\"hatching\">e</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l8l8\"><span class=\"transcription\">e</span></pb-popover> <span class=\"insertionMark right  insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">tritt</span></span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l8l11\" class=\"hatching\">steht</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l8l11\"><span class=\"transcription\">steht</span></pb-popover>: es \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb3\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb3\" duration=\"5000\">3</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">sind Zeiten der Ermüdung, oft des Abends, des Niederganges, – die überströmende <span class=\"insertion-above \"><span class=\"above instantaneous\" style=\"\">Kraft,</span></span><span class=\"tei-del15 strikethrough\">Ge-</span> \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb4\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb4\" duration=\"5000\">4</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\"><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l10l4\" class=\"hatching\">wiß</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l10l4\"><span class=\"transcription\">wiß</span></pb-popover>, die Lebens-Gewißheit, <span class=\"insertionMark right inSpatium insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">die</span></span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Zukunfts</span>-Gewißheit sind dahin. Das Übergewicht des Manda-\n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb5\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb5\" duration=\"5000\">5</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">rinen bedeutet niemals etwas Gutes: so wenig als die Heraufkunft der Demokratie, \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb6\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb6\" duration=\"5000\">6</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">der Friedens-Schiedsgerichte an Stelle der Kriege, <span class=\"insertionMark right  insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">der Frauen-Gleichberechtigung,</span></span> der Religion des Mitleids und was \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb7\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb7\" duration=\"5000\">7</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">es <span class=\"insertionMark right inSpatium insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">sonst</span></span> Alles für Symptome des absinkenden Lebens <span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l13l7\" class=\"hatching\">*s</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l13l7\"><span class=\"transcription\">*s</span></pb-popover> giebt. <span class=\"insertionMark right  insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">(Wissenschaft als Problem gefaßt; was bedeutet Wissenschaft? – vergl. darüber die Vorrede zur „<span class=\"latin\">Geburt der Tragödie</span>“)</span></span> – Nein! diese „moderne \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb8\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb8\" duration=\"5000\">8</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">Wissenschaft“ – macht euch <span class=\"insertionMark right inSpatium insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">nur</span></span> dafür die Augen auf! – ist <span class=\"insertionMark right inSpatium insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">einstweilen</span></span> die <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">beste</span> Bundesgenossin des aske-\n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb9\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb9\" duration=\"5000\">9</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">tischen Ideals, und gerade deshalb, weil sie die unbewußteste, die unfreiwilligste, die \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb10\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb10\" duration=\"5000\">10</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">heimlichste und unterirdischeste ist! Sie haben bis jetzt Ein Spiel gespielt, die „Armen \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb11\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb11\" duration=\"5000\">11</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">des Geistes“ und die wissenschaftlichen <span class=\"insertionMark right  insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">Widersacher</span></span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l17l6\" class=\"hatching\">Gegner</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l17l6\"><span class=\"transcription\">Gegner</span></pb-popover> jenes Ideals (<span class=\"insertionMark right inWord insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">man hüte sich <span class=\"insertionMark right inSpatium insertion-below \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"below \" style=\"\">anbei gesagt,</span></span> zu denken, daß sie deren Gegen-</span></span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l17l9\" class=\"hatching\">ich hüte mich zu sagen, daß sie</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l17l9\"><span class=\"transcription\">ich hüte mich zu sagen, daß sie</span></pb-popover> \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb12\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb12\" duration=\"5000\">12</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\"><span class=\"insertionMark right  insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">satz seien, etwa als </span></span>die <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Reichen</span> des Geistes<span class=\"inline   \"> –</span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l18l9\" class=\"hatching\">, die „Geistreichen“</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l18l9\"><span class=\"transcription\">, die „Geistreichen“</span></pb-popover><span class=\"inline   \"><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l18l10l3\" class=\"hatching\">*…</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l18l10l3\"><span class=\"transcription\">*…</span></pb-popover></span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l18l11\" class=\"hatching\">seien…</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l18l11\"><span class=\"transcription\">seien…</span></pb-popover><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l18l12\" class=\"strikethrough\">)</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l18l12\"><span class=\"transcription\">)</span></pb-popover><span class=\"insertionMark right beforePunctuation insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\"> das sind sie <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">nicht</span>, ich nannte sie Hektiker des Geistes)</span></span>. <span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l18l15\" class=\"hatching\">Man sehe sich</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l18l15\"><span class=\"transcription\">Man sehe sich</span></pb-popover> <pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"b59r_add_d2e188\" style=\"\"><p><span style=\"font-style: italic;\"><pb-i18n key=\"myapp.overwritten\">\n                            überschrieben\n                          </pb-i18n>:</span><span class=\"transkriptionField small \">d</span></p></pb-popover><span class=\"trigger popover\" id=\"b59r_add_d2e188\" data-debug=\"add4\"><span class=\"inline  \">D</span></span>iese <span class=\"insertionMark right  insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">berühmten</span></span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l18l21\" class=\"hatching\">angeblichen</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l18l21\"><span class=\"transcription\">angeblichen</span></pb-popover> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Siege</span> \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb13\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb13\" duration=\"5000\">13</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">der letzteren<span class=\"inline   \">:</span> <span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l19l7\" class=\"hatching\">doch aus der Nähe an:</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l19l7\"><span class=\"transcription\">doch aus der Nähe an:</span></pb-popover> <span class=\"insertionMark right inSpatium insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">unzweifelhaft,</span></span> es sind Siege – aber worüber? Das asketische I-\n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb14\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb14\" duration=\"5000\">14</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">deal <span class=\"insertionMark right  insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">wurde</span></span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l20l6\" class=\"hatching\">ist</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l20l6\"><span class=\"transcription\">ist</span></pb-popover> ganz und gar nicht in ihnen besiegt, es <span class=\"insertionMark right  insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">wurde</span></span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l20l11\" class=\"hatching\">ist</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l20l11\"><span class=\"transcription\">ist</span></pb-popover> eher damit stärker, nämlich unfaßlicher, \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb15\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb15\" duration=\"5000\">15</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">geistiger, verfänglicher gemacht, daß immer wieder eine Mauer, ein Außenwerk, das sich an \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb16\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb16\" duration=\"5000\">16</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">dasselbe angebaut hatte und seinen Aspekt <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">vergröberte</span>, seitens der Wissenschaft schonungs-\n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb17\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb17\" duration=\"5000\">17</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">los abgelöst, abgebrochen <span class=\"insertionMark right  insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">worden ist.</span></span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l23l6\" class=\"hatching\">wird</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l23l6\"><span class=\"transcription\">wird</span></pb-popover>. Meint man in der That, daß <span class=\"insertionMark right inSpatium insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">etwa</span></span> die Niederlage der theologi-\n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb18\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb18\" duration=\"5000\">18</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">schen Astronomie eine Niederlage jenes Ideals bedeute?… Ist damit vielleicht der Mensch \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb19\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb19\" duration=\"5000\">19</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\"><span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">weniger</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">bedürftig</span> nach einer Jenseitigkeits-Lösung seines Räthsels von Dasein gewor-\n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb20\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb20\" duration=\"5000\">20</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">den, daß dieses Dasein sich seitdem noch beliebiger, eckensteherischer, entbehrlicher in \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb21\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb21\" duration=\"5000\">21</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">der <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">sichtbaren</span> Ordnung der Dinge ausnimmt? Ist nicht gerade die Selbstverkleinerung \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb22\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb22\" duration=\"5000\">22</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">des Menschen, sein <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Wille</span> zur Selbstverkleinerung <span class=\"insertionMark right  insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">seit Kopernikus</span></span> in einem unaufhaltsamen Fortschritte? \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb23\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb23\" duration=\"5000\">23</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">Ach, der Glaube an seine Würde, Einzigkeit<span class=\"inline   \">,</span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l29l6\" class=\"strikethrough\">,</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l29l6\"><span class=\"transcription\">,</span></pb-popover> Unersetzlichkeit in der Rangabfolge der We-\n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_b59r_lb24\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"b59r_lb24\" duration=\"5000\">24</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">sen ist dahin, – er ist <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Thier</span> geworden<span class=\"inline   \">,</span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l30l8\" class=\"strikethrough\">,</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l30l8\"><span class=\"transcription\">,</span></pb-popover><span class=\"insertionMark right afterWord insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"left:-14.4531em;top:-1.40627em;\">Thier, ohne Gleichniß<span class=\"inline   \">,</span><span class=\"insertionMark right afterWord insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"left:0em;top:-0.976554em;\"> Abzug</span></span> <span class=\"tei-choice5\">u</span> Vorbehalt,</span></span> er, der in <span class=\"insertionMark right  insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">seinem</span></span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l30l12\" class=\"hatching\">einem</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l30l12\"><span class=\"transcription\">einem</span></pb-popover> früheren <span class=\"insertion-above \"><span class=\"above \" style=\"left:-1.875em;top:-2.03126em;\">Glauben</span></span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l30l15\" class=\"hatching\">Falle</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l36l5l30l15\"><span class=\"transcription\">Falle</span></pb-popover> <span class=\"insertionMark right inSpatium insertion-above \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"\">beinahe</span></span> Gott <span class=\"insertionMark right inSpatium insertion-below \" style=\"\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"below \" style=\"left:-1.875em;top:1.79688em;\">(„Kind Gottes“, „Gottmensch<pb-popover theme=\"material\"><span slot=\"default\" class=\"choice choiceParent\"><span class=\"tei-sic1\">)“</span></span><template slot=\"alternate\"><p class=\"sicCor\"><span class=\"tei-sic1\">)“</span> &gt; <span class=\"tei-corr1\">“)</span></p></template></pb-popover></span></span> war… \n            </span></div><div id=\"srcD_zone_b59r_fw_d2e33\" class=\"fw-bottom-left\" style=\"\"></div></div></div></div></body></html>",
